    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. You\u2019ll find some typical signs of use here and there, but it still looks great and runs even better! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
