    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains sharp, benefitting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to maintain the integrity of its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent comprehensive service includes a VANOS overhaul and a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the high-compression engine operates at peak thermal efficiency. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, this example is mechanically robust and optimized for driver engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
