    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that screams to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanical integrity is prioritized, with the critical subframe reinforcement already completed and a recently overhauled VANOS system ensuring valve timing precision. The suspension maintains its composure through corners thanks to updated bushings and the factory-spec variable M differential lock providing excellent corner-exit traction. While the aesthetic reflects its history as a celebrated performance machine, the powertrain and chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. A mechanically robust specimen for the enthusiast who values analog feedback and engineering purity.",
